00:47:11.955 --> 00:47:12.956
Maybe so.

790
00:47:13.831 --> 00:47:16.668
I mean. when shit get ill.

791
00:47:18.127 --> 00:47:21.005
and it seem like...

792
00:47:22.799 --> 00:47:24.259
you ain't got nothin' left.

793
00:47:25.093 --> 00:47:26.469
you start prayin'.

794
00:47:27.554 --> 00:47:30.932
You ain't prayin' to the mayor
or the fuckin' president.

795
00:47:31.391 --> 00:47:33.476
or even Mama to save you.

796
00:47:34.185 --> 00:47:35.645
You prayin' to God.

797
00:47:36.229 --> 00:47:38.565
But maybe you prayin' like that
'cause you so pressed.

798
00:47:38.731 --> 00:47:40.608
start reachin' for shit that ain't true.

799
00:47:40.775 --> 00:47:43.611
Or maybe you so pressed that...

800
00:47:44.487 --> 00:47:46.072
you finally reach the truth.

801
00:47:49.742 --> 00:47:51.786
Shit. Fuck if I know.

802
00:47:51.911 --> 00:47:54.706
Just feel like I'm lookin'
for some shit I lost

803
00:47:55.456 --> 00:47:57.333
and I know I'm never gonna find it.

804
00:48:06.217 --> 00:48:07.510
Keep lookin' anyway.

805
00:48:10.972 --> 00:48:12.974
It ain't even about just Lou.

806
00:48:14.142 --> 00:48:16.227
It's about us. It's about everything.

807
00:48:17.437 --> 00:48:18.605
Maybe...

808
00:48:18.980 --> 00:48:20.440
we all lost. Raq.

809
00:48:21.107 --> 00:48:22.400
And maybe...

810
00:48:25.028 --> 00:48:26.613
we ain't never gon' be found.

811
00:48:51.512 --> 00:48:53.181
You do this shit long enough.

812
00:48:53.306 --> 00:48:54.891
one thing's for sure.

813
00:48:55.058 --> 00:48:57.143
Your circle gonna get
a hell of a lot smaller.

814
00:48:57.810 --> 00:49:00.313
You gon' lose damn near
every nigga you ever trusted.

815
00:49:00.480 --> 00:49:01.814
What's your name?

816
00:49:02.315 --> 00:49:04.525
Whatever you want it to be.

817
00:49:05.276 --> 00:49:06.569
And as tough as it is to lose

818
00:49:06.736 --> 00:49:08.279
all your old friends...

819
00:49:09.113 --> 00:49:10.823
the shit you really need to worry about

820
00:49:11.783 --> 00:49:13.117
is your new ones.

821
00:49:14.661 --> 00:49:16.454
'Cause you can't trust
new friends. nigga.

822
00:49:17.205 --> 00:49:18.205
Not ever.
